OL,3,CJersey schools saw 13 exclusions for
OL,4,C'offensive weapon' cases in 2024
OL,6,FThere were 13 exclusions from schools
OL,7,Fin Jersey last year over the threat or
OL,8,Fuse of 'offensive weapons' - a five-
OL,9,Fyear high.
OL,11,FAn ITV News Freedom of Information
OL,12,Frequest has revealed rising rates of
OL,13,Fracism, assaults against adults and
OL,14,Fuse or threats of weapon use by pupils
OL,15,Fsince 2020.
OL,17,FExclusions due to physical assaults
OL,18,Fagainst adults have also increased by
OL,19,F14% over the past five years.
