OL,3,CJersey schools saw 13 exclusions for
OL,4,C'offensive weapon' cases in 2024
OL,6,FThese statistics relate to incidents
OL,7,Fof exclusion, rather than the number
OL,8,Fof children who have been excluded,
OL,9,Fand include repeat offenders.
OL,11,FThere have been 12 instances over the
OL,12,Flast five years where exclusions have
OL,13,Fhad to be referred to the police.
OL,15,FHowever, there is better news with
OL,16,Fexclusions relating to drugs and
OL,17,Falcohol at just over a third of what
OL,18,Fthey were five years ago, shrinking
OL,19,Ffrom 117 to 45.
